{{!< default}}

<h2>Who we are</h2>
<p>We are a network of democracy practitioners, organisers, researchers and professionals committed to developing and
  defending democratic society.</p>

<h2>What we do</h2>
<p>The Democracy Network connects, strengthens and champions a dynamic network of people and civil society organisations
  working to strengthen and advance democracy in the UK.</p>

<div class="grid-container">
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">
      <header>
        <h2>Networking</h2>
      </header>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>We build spaces and opportunities for democracy practitioners to learn from each other, build trust and
          develop
          strategies together.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <header>
        <h3>Ecosystem</h3>
      </header>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>
          We provide access to shared resources, skills and intelligence

          More asset based approach etc, hubs stuff
        </p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <header>
        <h3>Infrastructure</h3>
      </header>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>We provide access to a shared information layer, combining resources, skills and intelligence - through which
          people
          working to strengthen democracy can better develop a sense of the field, their role and opportunities within
          it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{{#get "posts" limit="1" as |latest|}}
  {{#foreach latest}}
    <section class="latest-post" aria-label="Latest bulletin">
      <h2>Latest bulletins</h2>
      {{> "bulletin-card"}}
    </section>
  {{/foreach}}
{{/get}}
<div class="grid-container">
  <div class="grid">
    {{#get "posts" limit="4" offset="1" as |latest|}}
      {{#foreach latest}}
        {{#unless @first}}
          {{> "bulletin-card"}}
        {{/unless}}
      {{/foreach}}
    {{/get}}

  </div>
</div>

<p><a href="/bulletin/">See all bulletins →</a></p>

